      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0571P0-04871'>
        <a name='S5LV0571P0_19960424_GCR_71'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-neil-carmichael' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0571P0_19960424_GCR_71' title='Link to this speech by Mr Neil Carmichael' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
