        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0571P0_19960424_GCR_125' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Schedule 6 [<span class="italic">Repeals</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0571P0-04926'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0571P0_19960424_GCR_126' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Lord Carmichael of Kelvingrove</span> moved Amendment No. 47:
